# PED::SET_ENABLE_SCUBA

## Summary
Set whether scuba gear is equipped to adjust swimming behavior

## Parameters
* **PED_INDEX** ped
* **BOOL** enable

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Enables diving motion when underwater.
